@startuml 类图
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 14
skinparam classAttributeFontSize 12

title 书法报名系统核心类图

class FlaskApp << (A,#FFAAAA) >> {
  + app: Flask
  + socketio: SocketIO
  + static_folder: str
  + template_folder: str
  --
  + __init__()
}

class DatabaseConnection << (C,#ADD1B2) >> {
  - conn: sqlite3.Connection
  --
  + __enter__(): Connection
  + __exit__(exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb)
}

class RouteHandlers << (C,#ADD1B2) >> {
  -- 用户认证 --
  + login(): Response
  + register(): Response
  + logout(): Response
  + complete_profile(): Response
  + change_password(): JSON
  -- 课程管理 --
  + courses(): Response
  + course_detail(course_id): Response
  + add_course(): Response
  -- 报名缴费 --
  + enroll(course_id): JSON
  + payment(): JSON
  -- 管理后台 --
  + admin(): Response
  + attendance(course_id): Response
  + hours_management(): Response
  + move_student(): JSON
  + remove_student(): JSON
  + add_student(): JSON
  -- 消息通信 --
  + messages(): Response
  + send_message(): JSON
  + api_conversation(other_user_id): JSON
}

class WebSocketHandlers << (C,#ADD1B2) >> {
  + handle_connect()
  + handle_disconnect()
  + handle_join_course(data)
  + handle_leave_course(data)
  + handle_send_message(data)
  + handle_attendance_update(data)
  + handle_course_enrollment(data)
}

class SecurityUtils << (U,#FFE0A0) >> {
  + {static} hash_password(password: str): str
  + {static} verify_password(password, hashed): bool
  + {static} generate_captcha(return_base64): str/BytesIO
  + {static} check_captcha(user_input): bool
  + {static} validate_phone(phone): bool
  + {static} rate_limit(max_requests, window): decorator
}

class DatabaseInit << (C,#ADD1B2) >> {
  + {static} init_db()
  + {static} init_admin()
}

class ErrorHandlers << (C,#ADD1B2) >> {
  + not_found(error): Response
  + internal_error(error): Response
  + rate_limit_handler(error): Response
}

class DatabaseConnection {
  + __enter__()
  + __exit__(...)
}

FlaskApp --> RouteHandlers : routes
FlaskApp --> WebSocketHandlers : socketio events
FlaskApp --> ErrorHandlers : error handlers

RouteHandlers ..> DatabaseConnection : uses
RouteHandlers ..> SecurityUtils : uses
RouteHandlers ..> DatabaseInit : uses

WebSocketHandlers ..> DatabaseConnection : uses

note right of SecurityUtils
  安全工具类：
  - PBKDF2-HMAC-SHA256 密码哈希
  - 图形验证码生成与校验
  - 手机号格式验证
  - 请求频率限制装饰器
end note

note bottom of RouteHandlers
  主路由模块 app/routes/main.py
  包含所有 HTTP API 路由和
  WebSocket 事件处理函数
end note

@enduml